| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3278 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 90e69f79-2939-5e31-bd38-ec1ba394ae5d"
